00:20:18.477 --> 00:20:20.895
It can also
be worth waiting for.

518
00:20:20.896 --> 00:20:24.682
Jay, what is this?

519
00:20:24.683 --> 00:20:26.317
Just another nice thing
I did for you

520
00:20:26.318 --> 00:20:27.652
While you
made a fool of me.

521
00:20:27.653 --> 00:20:30.071
