522
00:20:30.072 --> 00:20:31.823
You feel bad now?

523
00:20:31.824 --> 00:20:33.324
No. I feel good.

524
00:20:36.528 --> 00:20:37.828
Mm.

525
00:20:40.666 --> 00:20:44.023
That one
is definitely my favorite.

526
00:20:46.457 --> 00:20:47.809
Phil, you really
don't have to do this.

527
00:20:47.810 --> 00:20:51.246
No. I-I can do it.
